### ✅ Flashcard — ĐẦY ĐỦ *(2026-04-16)*
| BE Endpoint | FE tRPC | Ghi chú |
|---|---|---|
| `PUT /api/flashcards/{id}` | `flashcard.edit` | ✅ |
| `POST /api/flashcards` | `flashcard.create` | ✅ |
| `DELETE /api/flashcards/{id}` | `flashcard.delete` | ✅ |
| `GET /api/studysets/{id}/flashcards` | nằm trong `studySet.byId` | ✅ |
| `POST /api/studysets/{id}/flashcards/import` | `flashcard.importExcel` + `ImportExcelDialog` | ✅ |
| `GET /api/studysets/{id}/flashcards/export` | `flashcard.exportExcel` + Download button | ✅ |
| `POST /api/flashcards/clone` | `flashcard.clone` + `CloneFlashcardsDialog` | ✅ |
| `GET /api/flashcards/import/template` | `flashcard.downloadTemplate` | ✅ |

**UI:** Toolbar Import/Export/Clone trên study set form + `FlashcardToolbar` (TTS/Translate/Spellcheck/Upload) mỗi card.

